 railway station|Coimbra]]'' |next= |rows2=2}}\n{{rail line |route=[[Comboios_de_Portugal#Services|Regional]] |col=FFA700 |previous= [[Vila Nova de Gaia railway station|Vila Nova de Gaia]]<br/><small>''toward [[Santa Apol\u00f3nia railway station|Lisboa-Santa Apol\u00f3nia]]'' |next= |hide2=yes}}\n{{rail line |route=[[Comboios_de_Portugal#Services|Regional]] |col=FFA700 |previous= [[S\u00e3o Bento Railway Station|Porto-S\u00e3o Bento]]<br/><small>''Terminus'' |next=[[Ermesinde railway station|Ermesinde]]<br/><small>''toward [[R\u00e9gua railway station|R\u00e9gua]]''}}\n{{rail line |route=[[Comboios_de_Portugal#Services|Regional]] |col=FFA700 |previous= |next=[[Ermesinde railway station|Ermesinde]]<br/><small>''toward [[Viana do Castelo railway station|Viana do Castelo]]''}}\n{{s-rail|title=CP Porto}}\n{{rail line |route=[[CP Porto|Linha do Marco]] |col=0083D7 |previous=[[S\u00e3o Bento Railway Station|Porto-S\u00e3o Bento]]<br/><small>''Terminus'' |next=[[Contumil railway station|Contumil]]<br/><small>''toward [[Marco de Canaveses railway station|Marco de Canaveses]]''|rows1=4}}\n{{rail line |route=[[CP Porto|Linha de Guimar\u00e3es]] |col=E62621 |previous=[[S\u00e3o Bento Railway Station|Porto-S\u00e3o Bento]]<br/><small>''Terminus'' |next=[[Contumil railway station|Contumil]]<br/><small>''toward [[Guimar\u00e3es railway station|Guimar\u00e3es]]''|hide1=yes}}\n{{rail line |route=[[CP Porto|Linha de Braga]] |col=00A550 |previous=[[S\u00e3o Bento Railway Station|Porto-S\u00e3o Bento]]<br/><small>''Terminus'' |next=[[Contumil railway station|Contumil]]<br/><small>''toward [[Braga railway station|Braga]]''|hide1=yes}}\n{{rail line |route=[[CP Porto|Linha de Aveiro]] |col=FFA700 |previous=[[S\u00e3o Bento Railway Station|Porto-S\u00e3o Bento]]<br/><small>''Terminus'' |next=[[General Torres railway station|General Torres]]<br/><small>''toward [[Aveiro railway station|Aveiro]]''|hide1=yes}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n==Porto Metro station==\n{{Infobox Station\n | name=Campanh\u00e3\n | type=[[Porto Metro]] station\n | logo=\n | logo_size=\n | image=Campanha 20120829.jpg\n | image_size=\n | image_caption=\n | coordinates=\n | address=Campanh\u00e3, [[Porto]]\n | country=[[Portugal]]\n | line=[[File:Metro do Porto linha A.svg|15px|link=Porto Metro]] [[File:Metro do Porto linha B.svg|15px|link=Porto Metro]] [[File:Metro do Porto linha C.svg|15px|link=Porto Metro]] [[File:Metro do Porto linha F.svg|15px|link=Porto Metro]]\n | other=\n | structure=At Grade\n | platform=2 [[side platforms]]\n | tracks=2\n | parking=\n | bicycle=\n | passengers=\n | pass_year=\n | pass_percent=\n | opened=5 June 2004\n | rebuilt=\n | ADA=Yes\n | code=\n | owned=\n | zone=\n | smartcardname = \n | smartcardstatus = \n | services=\n{{s-rail|title=Porto Metro}}\n{{rail line |route=[[Porto Metro#Network|Line A]] |col={{PTM color|A}} |previous=[[Hero\u00edsmo station|Hero\u00edsmo]]<br/><small>''toward [[Senhor de Matosinhos station|Senhor de Matosinhos]]''<small/>|next=[[Est\u00e1dio do Drag\u00e3o station|Est\u00e1dio do Drag\u00e3o]]<br/><small>''Terminus''<small/>|rows2=2}}\n{{rail line |route=[[Porto Metro#Network|Line B]] |col={{PTM color|B}} |previous=[[Hero\u00edsmo station|Hero\u00edsmo]]<br/><small>''toward [[P\u00f3voa de Varzim station|P\u00f3voa de Varzim]]''<small/>|next=[[Est\u00e1dio do Drag\u00e3o station|Est\u00e1dio do Drag\u00e3o]]<br/><small>''Terminus''<small/>|hide2=yes}}\n{{rail line |route=[[Porto Metro#Network|Line C]] |col={{PTM color|C}} |previous=[[Hero\u00edsmo station|Hero\u00edsmo]]<br/><small>''toward [[ISMAI station|ISMAI]]''<small/>|next= }}\n{{rail line |route=[[Porto Metro#Network|Line F]] |col={{PTM color|F}} |previous=[[Hero\u00edsmo station|Hero\u00edsmo]]<br/><small>''toward [[Senhora da Hora station|Senhora da Hora]]''<small/>|next=[[Est\u00e1dio do Drag\u00e3o station|Est\u00e1dio do Drag\u00e3o]]<br/><small>''toward [[F\u00e2nzeres station|F\u00e2nzeres]]''<small/>}}\n}}\nCampanh\u00e3 is an integral line within the [[Porto Metro|Metro do Porto]], except Line D; all these services route through the station. Campanh\u00e3 is also the terminal hub of Line C, which connects the station to ISMAI (''Instituto Universit\u00e1rio da Maia''). Passenger trams stopping at Campanh\u00e3 allow offload to other routes, but farther beyond the terminal station for visitors to the [[Est\u00e1dio do Drag\u00e3o]] and railyard.\n\n==References==\n===Notes===\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n===Sources===\n* {{citation |last=Martins |first=Jo\u00e3o Paulo |title=Cottinelli Telmo. A Obra do Arquitecto (1897-1948). Disserta\u00e7\u00e3o de mestrado em Hist\u00f3ria da Arte |location=Lisbon, Portugal |publisher=FCSH/University of Lisbon |year=1995 |language=Portuguese}}\n* {{citation |last=Ramos |first=Lu\u00eds A. de Oliveira |title=Hist\u00f3ria do Porto |location=Porto, Portugal |publisher=Porto Editora |year=1994 |language=Portuguese}}\n\n{{Porto}}\n{{Porto Metro navbox|state=collapsed}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Campanha station}}\n[[Category:Porto Metro stations]]\n[[Category:Railway stations in Porto]]\n[[Category:Railway stations opened in 1877]]\n[[Category:1877 establishments in Portugal]]\n", "name_user": "Tholme", "label": "safe", "comment": "lintfix", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Campanh%C3%A3_railway_station"}
